@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home Page";
}
<div class="jumbotron text-center" style="padding-top: 15rem">
    <h1>QuickFix</h1>
    <p>Convenience at your fingertips!</p>
    <form>
        <div class="input-group">
            <input type="email" class="form-control" size="50" placeholder="Email Address" required>
            <div class="input-group-btn">
                <button type="button" class="btn btn-danger">Subscribe</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </form>
</div>
<div class="container" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-4">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-globe"></span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-sm-8">
            <h2 style="color:white">How it Works</h2><br>
            <p>
                <strong>Preventative Maintenance has never been easier</strong>Avoid the hassle of driving your car or having it towed to a service center. Time is valuable and so are our vehicles, which is why we make the entire process easy for you as the customer
                or you as the business owner. Using our website or our mobile apps, you can access all local companies that partner with us and their availabilities.
                We keep the price fair and transparent, enable future scheduling with reminders, offer payment options through the application, accessible service history and most importantly live updates and tracking features. Check one more task off
                your list and use that time to focus on the more important things in life.
            </p><br>
            <p>
                <strong>Schedule your first appointment today!</strong> You as the client have the option to not only select your preferred service provider, but set time requirements when filling out our request details form.
                Misunderstandings or Unhappy service from either parties, Our 24 hour customer service is ready to address any concerns.
                A full report of service details will be accessible and saved to your profile for future providers to see or to file away as you see fit
            </p>
            <button class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Start Today!</button>
        </div>

    </div>
</div>


